data.description: This warm and inviting 5 bedroom 2 bath stunner sits on a .5 acre oversized Corner lot.  This home includes vaulted ceilings, beautiful screened pool, & converted garage. Bahama shutters, amazing palm trees & extra long driveway give this home the curb appeal you have been looking for. The home features a water filtration system w/reverse osmosis system, updated SS appliances, NO carpet, ceiling fans throughout, screened patio with speakers and tv, ring doorbell, & smart lock, 2 sheds (stay with the home), & vinyl fencing. Master bath w/ dual sinks, separate tub & shower. White Vinyl fence to be installed behind the new construction house & neighboring property by their owner to add privacy.
